    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Vegetable oil extracted from the seed kernel of the peanut. The oil is edible and used for cooking, but is also used in soaps and fuels.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
